#: ../../installation.rst:2 bcbff2e28ac4457a84ffc63c7995485a
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../installation.rst:4 d75f2ccd709140738165b845f4227761
msgid ""
"This page covers all supported installation methods for VoxCPM. If you "
"just want the fastest path to get started, see :doc:`./quickstart`."
msgstr "本页涵盖 VoxCPM 的所有受支持安装方式。如果你只想最快开始使用，请查看 :doc:`./quickstart`。"

#: ../../installation.rst:7 54b6bcde97ae497785547abfcca02257
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "环境要求"

#: ../../installation.rst:13 eede858e782c4652aa2c3b7da33bc844
msgid "Dependency"
msgstr "依赖项"

#: ../../installation.rst:14 4f83b76bf4c6403a89b4a84ce476edf0
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../installation.rst:15 86686502cdee4d33bb90bb326023ccb0
msgid "PyTorch"
msgstr "PyTorch"

#: ../../installation.rst:16 e03b8b14444b447892ad98c59b2b727c
msgid "2.5.0 or higher"
msgstr "2.5.0 或更高"

#: ../../installation.rst:17 bc0cf8f8bafb4f90aa19071975e739cf
msgid "CUDA"
msgstr "CUDA"

#: ../../installation.rst:18 81912afe33f0416eaffb4457e7a45731
msgid "Optional. 12.0 or higher for NVIDIA GPU acceleration"
msgstr "可选。若使用 NVIDIA GPU 加速，建议 12.0 或更高版本"

#: ../../installation.rst:19 2654572d76474e409527229147d7b155
msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

#: ../../installation.rst:20 a70e53cf96514a5b9cefbd4320958e17
msgid "3.10–3.12 recommended (3.10–3.11 most tested)"
msgstr "推荐 3.10–3.12（其中 3.10–3.11 测试最充分）"

#: ../../installation.rst:21 3854ac9045e64656b5e01b7d45ac12fe
msgid "Disk Space"
msgstr "磁盘空间"

#: ../../installation.rst:22 3426bee23ff540f2be72c2637750bca1
msgid "Several GBs for model weights, depending on the checkpoint you use"
msgstr "模型权重需要数 GB 空间，具体取决于你使用的 checkpoint"

#: ../../installation.rst:26 e9228d698e4749deac72809b8681ecd1
msgid ""
"CUDA is not required for CPU inference or Apple Silicon MPS usage. See "
":doc:`./faq` for Mac / MPS notes."
msgstr ""
"如果你使用 CPU 推理或 Apple Silicon MPS，则不需要 CUDA。有关 Mac / MPS 的说明请参阅 "
":doc:`./faq`。"

#: ../../installation.rst:29 374ccebbb9bc4ec39bcafa62308286e6
msgid "Runtime Device Selection"
msgstr "运行时设备选择"

#: ../../installation.rst:31 863d714cec1c4ab4999beaa515bd77d3
msgid ""
"VoxCPM supports automatic device selection and explicit device forcing in"
" both the Python API and the CLI."
msgstr "VoxCPM 在 Python API 和 CLI 中都支持自动选择设备，以及显式强制指定设备。"

#: ../../installation.rst:34 155a9be335de4340867aa24be91b8b23
msgid "Automatic selection"
msgstr "自动选择"

#: ../../installation.rst:36 0a520244160c43d9b23d9247fa672698
msgid "``device=None`` or ``device=\"auto\"`` uses automatic fallback"
msgstr "``device=None`` 或 ``device=\"auto\"`` 会使用自动回退逻辑"

#: ../../installation.rst:37 65d55cf57f294a7ca08918df54f12837
msgid "The fallback order is ``cuda -> mps -> cpu``"
msgstr "回退顺序为 ``cuda -> mps -> cpu``"

#: ../../installation.rst:38 3cef1f099dcd4a4da565e1d71e07d002
msgid "The CLI uses the same behavior through ``--device auto``"
msgstr "CLI 通过 ``--device auto`` 使用相同的行为"

#: ../../installation.rst:40 fc40b51a70db4547a9e5c9a731f7fbd7
msgid "Explicit selection"
msgstr "显式指定"

#: ../../installation.rst:42 25ab66712e0d4bfcbde091a5c52a8c6b
msgid "``device=\"cpu\"`` forces CPU inference"
msgstr "``device=\"cpu\"`` 会强制使用 CPU 推理"

#: ../../installation.rst:43 ca5b1ee71c924147b9ff699abb0bf09d
msgid "``device=\"mps\"`` forces Apple Silicon MPS"
msgstr "``device=\"mps\"`` 会强制使用 Apple Silicon MPS"

#: ../../installation.rst:44 9ebfccb4221b4f75b439805cf729b22d
msgid "``device=\"cuda\"`` or ``device=\"cuda:N\"`` forces CUDA"
msgstr "``device=\"cuda\"`` 或 ``device=\"cuda:N\"`` 会强制使用 CUDA"

#: ../../installation.rst:45 f16419397475416fa5ee490135ffff8d
msgid ""
"Explicit device requests do **not** auto-fallback; if the requested "
"backend is unavailable, VoxCPM raises an error so the failure is visible"
msgstr "显式指定设备时**不会**自动回退；如果所请求的后端不可用，VoxCPM 会直接抛错，以便明确暴露问题。"

#: ../../installation.rst:62 749ea67f0fff4491b73e099d66ea9873
msgid ""
"``optimize=True`` enables ``torch.compile`` acceleration and is primarily"
" useful on CUDA. On CPU, MPS, ROCm, or other non-standard environments, "
"you may need ``optimize=False`` or CLI ``--no-optimize`` for "
"compatibility."
msgstr ""
"``optimize=True`` 会启用 ``torch.compile`` 加速，主要对 CUDA 场景有意义。"
"在 CPU、MPS、ROCm 或其它非标准环境中，为了兼容性你可能需要使用 ``optimize=False`` 或 CLI 的 "
"``--no-optimize``。"

#: ../../installation.rst:67 3897ed54be3b47f6b908705d38aea134
msgid "Install with pip (recommended)"
msgstr "使用 pip 安装（推荐）"

#: ../../installation.rst:69 a1d022bd492047daa676168afe7c4fb4
msgid ""
"``pip`` is the default recommended way to install VoxCPM. It keeps setup "
"simple and matches the most common Python workflow."
msgstr "``pip`` 是安装 VoxCPM 的首选方式。它配置简单，也最符合常见的 Python 使用习惯。"

#: ../../installation.rst:71 ../../installation.rst:90
#: 2c1b93d9521f4b1187d3e65d2011d32c 3aef1800a7c546a18bd523b7fe77b98d
msgid "From PyPI:"
msgstr "从 PyPI 安装："

#: ../../installation.rst:77 d5db1c389ccb4fd6a723f107499534fa
msgid "From source:"
msgstr "从源码安装："

#: ../../installation.rst:86 31831ab800b64ef18a7d3e6dee4c386e
msgid "Install with uv (secondary option)"
msgstr "使用 uv 安装（备选）"

#: ../../installation.rst:88 65a83399cc73450c9c0440220f2ef97c
msgid ""
"`uv <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/>`_ is a good secondary option if you "
"prefer a managed environment and faster dependency resolution."
msgstr ""
"`uv <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/>`_ "
"也是一个不错的次选方案，适合希望用工具统一管理环境、并获得更快依赖解析速度的用户。"

#: ../../installation.rst:96 3c34a8fd14264c7b9375a098f62425c5
msgid "From source (needed for running the web demo or local development):"
msgstr "从源码安装（运行 Web Demo 或本地开发时需要）："

#: ../../installation.rst:106 5bcc71997b7e4817baf52d816192d98d
msgid ""
"If you installed via ``uv sync``, run scripts with ``uv run`` to use the "
"managed environment. For example: ``uv run python app.py``, ``uv run "
"python scripts/train_voxcpm_finetune.py ...``."
msgstr ""
"如果你通过 ``uv sync`` 安装，请使用 ``uv run`` 运行脚本，以确保使用 `uv` 管理的环境。例如：``uv run "
"python app.py``、``uv run python scripts/train_voxcpm_finetune.py ...``。"

#: ../../installation.rst:110 6fa3783230e746638707c7d91756825f
msgid "The source installation is required if you want to:"
msgstr "如果你想进行以下操作，则需要从源码安装："

#: ../../installation.rst:112 afe8aca87c544def9ae7a8251673e477
msgid "run the local web demo (``python app.py``)"
msgstr "运行本地 Web Demo（``python app.py``）"

#: ../../installation.rst:113 ee3acd53bc8a4a8ba894c984db9eeb03
msgid "modify VoxCPM source code"
msgstr "修改 VoxCPM 源代码"

#: ../../installation.rst:114 564742803291479a9eb87d6a2ef59126
msgid "contribute to the project"
msgstr "参与项目贡献"

#: ../../installation.rst:117 f0912d0fc7e14043aed96eb39041f745
msgid "Hugging Face mirror"
msgstr "Hugging Face 镜像"

#: ../../installation.rst:119 d15191a638ac4fe1bbbad6b4083235e2
msgid ""
"If you have trouble accessing Hugging Face directly (common in some "
"regions), set the mirror before running any script:"
msgstr "如果你无法直接访问 Hugging Face（某些地区较常见），请在运行任何脚本前先设置镜像："

#: ../../installation.rst:125 b169294776234a8998556828e9b2d09e
msgid "Model weights will then be downloaded through the mirror automatically."
msgstr "之后模型权重会自动通过镜像下载。"

#: ../../installation.rst:128 64bd7e86956c40fe8adcfaf80ca984c1
msgid "Verify installation"
msgstr "验证安装是否成功"

#: ../../installation.rst:130 257c133e666a465596bfd2c12eac12cc
msgid "After installing, run a quick check:"
msgstr "安装完成后，运行一个快速检查："

#: ../../installation.rst:136 e6dcd61617e94e3cbc58067a555fe28e
msgid "If this prints without errors, your installation is working."
msgstr "如果这条命令能够无报错输出，说明你的安装已正常工作。"

